      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STAR BLING (2) drops back to a sprinting trip in his stable debut and will appreciate the anticipated tempo. Has form in NSW that lines up quite well for this. Stuck on gamely in testing conditions last time at Nowra over the mile, that followed a win at Sapphire Coast the start prior. Ideally placed and can make a bright start in the new colours. ZATANNA (5) is mixing her form but is a speedy mare on her day and gets in light with the 3kg claimer engaged. Expect her to find the front and take some catching. OUR DIVINYL (4) is another speedy galloper that will be giving himself every chance up on speed. Drawn to advantage on the quick back-up and will give backers a sight. COSTLESS (1) travelled just behind the leader before taking over and scoring a determined win by a head here last time over 1100m. Found winning form and can go on with it now. ALL CLUBS (3) hasn't won for a long time for a long time but is one to keep in mind for exotics.",
